MISCELLANEOUS DOCKET

92-1965. In re Margules.

Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. I(8)(H), the license of Ivy Marilyn Margules, Attorney Registration No. 0043999, is revoked. See In re Chavez (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1459, 580 N.E.2d 440, and In re Finesmith (1991), 62 Ohio St.3d 1460, 580 N.E.2d 441.

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Holmes, Douglas, Wright, H. Brown and Resnick, JJ., concur.
